<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Brunn, Bischof von Würzburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt Bereitschaft zum Austrag mit Eberhard von Thüngfeld mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_536" id="267v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_536_r1l14"><expan>Johanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> Byſchof cʒu <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_536_r1l15"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l16"><expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Tünfelt wegen / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l18">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd wiewol das iſt / daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_536_line_1576311866666_2729">ſich </ab></add> derſelb 
<del rend="strikethrough">Erber </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l20"><expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_536_r1l19">wider </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gen </del> vns vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> den </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_536_line_1576311907365_2765">dıe </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etvvaʒ vaſt <expan>vergriffe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l21">getan hat <expan>vnbıllıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache / Alſo / daʒ vvir des gen Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l22">niht verſchuldet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / doch ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir ew das vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l23">hinheim geſecʒt vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade damit geert als wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l24"><expan>cʒimlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / vnd wöllen <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Tünfelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l26">vnd der ~ ſeinen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_536_r1l25">für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> vmb alle vergangen ſach dıe ſich von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l27"><expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Eb<ex>erharts</ex></expan> wegen gen vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bıſʒ auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l28">den <expan>hewtige<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>verloffe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gut freund ſein 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l29">ongeuerde / vnd Jn keins argen darümb <expan>gevvarte<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_536_r1l30">wo etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_536" id="267v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Johanse<ex>n</ex></expan>, byschof czu
                            <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
                        von Tünfelt wegen, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n;</ex></expan> und wiewol das ist, daz
                            <add>sich</add> derselb <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
<add>wider</add> uns und <add>die</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwaz vast <expan>vergriffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und getan hat <expan>unbillich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache, also daz wir des
                        gen im niht verschuldet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> doch so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew das vormals hinheim geseczt und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade damit geert, als wol
                                <expan>czimlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist; und wöllen
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Tünfelt und der seinen <add>für uns und
                            die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add> umb alle vergangen sach, die
                        sich von <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eb<ex>erharts</ex></expan> wegen gen uns und den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bisz auf den
                            <expan>hewtige<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>verloffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, gut freund sein on geverde und in keins argen
                        darümb <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und wo etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
